data.title: Robert Randolph Band
data.text:
Enjoy a FREE concert on the Square from Robert Randolph Band!

Robert Randolph Band will take the Fifth Third Bank Center Stage on Fountain Square on Sunday, June 23rd with Lauren Eylise and The Perfect Children. Event runs from 6-9pm.

üç£üçîüçπ FOOD: Be sure to visit a nearby restaurant for dinner before or after the show! The area offers everything from fast-casual to fine dining. Click here to see what's nearby: https://bit.ly/3XkhrQ8

üöó PARKING: Secure Parking is available at a number of nearby garages including the Fountain Square Garage located at 520 Vine Street with vehicular entrances on Vine and Walnut streets, the 84.51 garage at 120 W. 5th Street, with entrances on both 5th and 6th Streets, or the 4th & Race garage at 411 Race Street with entrances on Elm and Race streets

üéü ENTRY: No tickets or reservations are required for this free show! 3CDC and Fifth Third Bank are excited to offer year round programming at Fountain Square. Thank you to our partners The City of Cincinnati, Visit Cincy, and Hamilton Country for enhancing programming on the Square in 2024.
